            </rs>. The master of the shop was a 
               <persName id="t16761011-1-victim2" type="victimName">
                     <rs id="t16761011-1-viclabel3" type="occupation">Watchmaker</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t16761011-1-victim2 t16761011-1-viclabel3"></join>
